{"tid":1693454,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"11.24區議會 你可以做....","createTime":"2019-11-04T15:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T04:40:12.000Z","uid":36807,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3e250f3976722911810791172ef57907d4402a","tid":1693454,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"諗到有幾點可以一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. Direct message宣傳<br />\n [FB,IG,WHATSAPP,AIR DROP....]</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你可以整一段訊息 單獨send俾不同朋友  <br />\n直接send訊息佢哋會認真睇嘅機會比較大 <br />\n例子: （唔好介意我用emoji，一般人用慣睇慣）<br />\n<br />\nHello XX ,我係 XXX <br />\n❗️嚟緊11月24日區選 ❗️<br />\n✨由7:30AM到10:30PM✨<br />\n拎身分證去相關票站投票就可以㗎啦 <br />\n好簡單亦都好快完成<br />\n<br />\n呢區可以選擇投： X號 XXX<br />\n佢嘅理念立場都比較好<br />\n<br />\n😚希望你可以抽時間去投票 <br />\n ❌勿投建制派勿投民建聯勿投保皇黨❌<br />\n因為選出嚟嘅議員將會代表你個區<br />\n亦會代表你嘅身份係區議會投票 <br />\n決定香港未來政策 資源分配等等<br />\n<br />\n投票係公民責任 <br />\n🇭🇰請運用你嘅權利為香港未來着想<br />\n☺️請你抽時間去投票 多謝你<br />\n<br />\n💡如果方便最好早啲去 <br />\n因為一來可以避免人哋用你身份投票<br />\n[2016已經發生過]<br />\n及避免政府突然間以社會秩序混亂等藉口終止投票<br />\n<br />\n💡通常票站門口會有香港調查協會做問卷<br />\n係親共 幫保皇黨配票/或者睇下邊度需要催票 <br />\n答佢投左民建聯/9UP就得 分數唔好俾滿分 會太假<br />\n<br />\n💡比多D資料你參考:<br />\n1️⃣我係咪選民?  資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=26ebec56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n(如果你真係未成為選民嘅話都唔緊要  幫我share 呢段俾你嘅選民朋友 多謝)<br />\n--勿投建制派 勿投民建聯 勿投保皇黨--<br />\n2️⃣候選人資料庫:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=66cc7ef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/</a><br />\n3️⃣現屆區議會勢力分布:<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk%2F&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=cb62dced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（比較得閒可以係呢段訊息打埋 你朋友個名<br />\n心理學上佢應該會更加留意）</span><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">24號當日一早約屋企人食個靚早餐再一齊去投票<br />\n分享下你想投邊個 叫埋你屋企人一齊投</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&mdash;-----------------------------------------------<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>幫手監察選舉運作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就住違規行為報料</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1693229/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1693229/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n「選舉觀察計劃」報料熱線 Election Observation Hotline<br />\nTelegram: @hotline19hkeop<br />\nWhatsApp: +85297424472<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>其他有用POST :</strong><br />\n【區選攻略】(即日至投票日)  BY日賣百份<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1691530/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1691530/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"545b611c924c8cc36d7c8c3a6f5f0bc992c3e2ba","tid":1693454,"uid":36807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"補充：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">選舉事務處，會於本月寄出「投票通知卡」。<br />\n請各選民務必留意有關來函，核對個人身份。如收到不明人士用了你的地址，請參閱選舉事務處職員的建議(見LINK)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24594/2019%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-24594/%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F24594%2F2019%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-24594%2F%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=a1311539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24594/2019%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-24594/%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99</a>"},{"pid":"05705048ae8766d7ed05ca365155a526a2034a8c","tid":1693454,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"Share文宣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FN5pJuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFN5pJuh.jpg&h=e9a42c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdCb7VY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdCb7VY.jpg&h=ffd0b4fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JbgzA0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JbgzA0.jpg&h=0cbe8d65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vm3F1f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvm3F1f2.jpg&h=3c26847b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcf6f6aec9778cffea3791d1aa1756701d87c4ae","tid":1693454,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gk8rctR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGk8rctR.jpg&h=ac07fecd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSiOqOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSiOqOR.jpg&h=d8738d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7i6WVx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7i6WVx.jpg&h=6888e486&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dN6kgVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdN6kgVz.jpg&h=00a601c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUAdBVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUAdBVA.jpg&h=63cd408a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AK6oY8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAK6oY8X.jpg&h=bd5f5a76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8Cb72i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8Cb72i.jpg&h=f48e8d4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af0e085af212245ef825fa5b1f20e5abdf0860d3","tid":1693454,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"仲可以幫手fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[文宣入] [街坊入] 2019 區議會選舉 1098 個參選人已上線，以下開放 Fact check<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662979</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"52df798b5c66d9c78dc7336b96fcaf164bd4e2b1","tid":1693454,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T22:46:15.000Z","msg":"［文宣貼紙］點解你班連登仔會識用貼紙嚟做文宣架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1688564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1688564</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GT6ZbH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GT6ZbH.jpg&h=82224b88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mB6MeK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmB6MeK2.jpg&h=f961aea8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c786f85f470f4a6d6e8ac04b544ee1063d01f569","tid":1693454,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T23:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1749ce0d78e7380177b1cd2bae8f481f5ad1865f","tid":1693454,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T23:12:26.000Z","msg":"區選無比例代表制點配票"},{"pid":"bc4fd751f91f00e450a842577062717ba20b